Setting up cross compiler:

Method 1: Making your own, refer to Beaglebone board cross compiler doc for steps.
-Make sure architecture and other variables are set for raspberry pi 3

Method 2: Buildroot: git clone https://git.buildroot.net/buildroot   , checkout 2024.02

-use the defconfig in buildroot
make raspberrypi3_defconfig

-open toolchain settings in menu
-enable install glibc utilities and C++ support

